DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to compare the pharmacokinetics of DP-R207 (Rosuvastatin 10mg and Ezetimibe 10mg fixed dose combinations) in comparison to each component administered alone in health male volunteers.
DOC.brief_title: A Study to Compare the Pharmacokinetics of DP-R207 in Comparison to Each Component Administered Alone
DOC.criteria: Healthy male subjects age between 19 and 55 signed informed consent subjects have an allergy reaction of this drug
